QuestData.Title: It's Ours Now
QuestData.Description: Only the strongest and foulest Vilebranch are left now. The soul eaters and blood drinkers, foul worshippers of the evil god Hakkar.$B$BThey are FOOLS! They cling to old, defeated beliefs. I won't tolerate their crimes against the Revantusk any longer.$B$BStrike the final blow. Claim Jintha'Alor for the Revantusk... claim it for the Horde!
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill 5 Vilebranch Blood Drinkers and 5 Vilebranch Soul Eaters in Jintha'Alor.
QuestData.CompletionText: You'll be quite busy if you want to spill as much blood as they have.
QuestData.RewardText: There are none left to oppose the Revantusk! Any stragglers will be quickly taken care of.$B$BYou've done my people a great honor, $n.
